%% Note: Audit/history reads and dry-run branch are omitted for clarity.
%%{init: {'theme': 'base', 'themeVariables': {'primaryColor': '#eef2ff', 'primaryTextColor': '#1e293b', 'primaryBorderColor': '#6366f1', 'lineColor': '#94a3b8', 'secondaryColor': '#ecfdf5', 'tertiaryColor': '#fffbeb', 'background': '#ffffff', 'mainBkg': '#f8fafc', 'nodeBorder': '#cbd5e1', 'clusterBkg': '#f1f5f9', 'clusterBorder': '#e2e8f0', 'titleColor': '#1e293b', 'edgeLabelBackground': '#ffffff', 'textColor': '#334155'}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    participant API as Feeds API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Queue as Redis Queue
    participant Worker as Feed Sync Worker
    participant Feed as HTTPS Feed
    participant Apply as xdpgw-apply
    participant Maps as Pinned BPF Maps

    Admin->>API: POST /feeds/{id}/sync
    API->>DB: Create FeedSyncRun + AgentJob
    DB-->>API: Commit
    API->>Queue: Dispatch job ID after commit
    API-->>Admin: 202 queued
    Queue->>Worker: Deliver FEED_SYNC
    Worker->>DB: Claim job and run
    Worker->>Feed: Stream HTTPS GET (capped, no redirect)

    alt Fetch fails, exceeds cap, or has zero valid entries
        Feed-->>Worker: Error or unusable body
        Worker->>DB: Mark failed and keep assertions/desired state
        Note right of Maps: Active slot and version remain unchanged
    else Valid or partial body
        Feed-->>Worker: Line-list bytes
        Worker->>DB: Lock state and reconcile assertions
        Worker->>DB: Record overlaps, counts, desired digest
        alt Desired digest already active
            Worker->>DB: Mark success or partial without swap
        else Global set requires convergence
            Worker->>Apply: Global snapshot + expected revision
            Apply->>Maps: Lock helper and read active slot/version
            Apply->>Maps: Carry service maps and rebuild global maps
            alt Build or verify fails
                Apply-->>Worker: Nonzero without flip
                Worker->>DB: Mark failed with active digest unchanged
            else Verify passes
                Apply->>Maps: Single active_config flip
                Apply-->>Worker: New slot and node-map version
                Worker->>DB: Mark active digest and run terminal state
            end
        end
    end
